DESCRIPTION
This title is new generation 3D action shooting game that exceeded any past game machines. A player can control realistic armed robot intuitively by touch panel control and any player can experience impressive battle scenes easily. To accomplish missions, the player destroy numerous enemies with get arms. The player can customizes player's robot (armed destroyer) to reinforce the robot repeatedly and challenge more higher,severe missions and mighty boss!
